Centrica Buys U.S. Energy Retailer First Choice for $270 Million

-- B y   W i l l   K e n n e d y
-- 
2011-09-23T06:05:50Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-23/centrica-buys-u-s-energy-retailer-first-choice-for-270-million.html
Centrica Plc (CNA) , the U.K. largest
power supplier, acquired Texas-based energy retailer First
Choice Power for $270 million in cash.  First choice has 220,000 residential and commercial
electricity customer accounts in  Texas , Centrica said in a
statement today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
 Will Kennedy  at 
 wkennedy3@bloomberg.net  